name: "We Love Big Tiddys"
description:
This piece is based on my unadulterated appreciation for breasts and those that share this fondness.. but it is not only big breasts that I love, but any pair of symmetric breasts with a nicely curved aesthetic.  The female human body is marvel of mankind and to deny or be ashamed of this is to be ashamed of humanity itself.  

There are those that would love to denigrate or "cancel" me for this type of expression, or for even using the word "tiddys/titties" etc, but "breasts" is not a raw word.  Expression should be raw.  My art doesn't wear bow ties or sip champagne. My art walks he streets and puts money in the cups of the downtrodden.  I am Kudaan and I love you all. If you understand me, then this piece is for you.

Digital Painting, 2021
